game.name: Halloween Differences
game.description:
You are crazy for celebrating the Halloween festival. Do not need to wait for the Halloween day, join Halloween Differences to enjoy and feel the wonderful moments of the occasion in your own style. We have got you covered with a brand new arcade game where you only need to spot the differences between the Halloween images. Solving these tricky puzzles is not going to be easier as they look similar at the first sight, but you find differences between them after looking properly.  

Find all seven differences in multiple levels of this fun and education puzzle challenge! You have to put your observation and concentration abilities to the test to spot all 7 differences in different and challenging 10 levels. Be careful and try to be fast as you would only be given one minute time to complete each level! These images cover different objects like ghosts, cats, pumpkins and witches. All these images would remind the lovely moments of the Halloween. Celebrate the Halloween night party in your own style!

In these pictures, haunted houses are prepared and located in amusement parks or you can see the schools decorated with pumpkins and other scary objects. Get ready to notice the Children who try to disguise themselves and right at the doors to ask for their favorite candy in this html5 puzzle game! Do you think that you are capable enough to spot all the differences between the pictures in this one of this best Halloween difference games for kids? Give it a try and have lots of fun without download on atmegame.com!
